EFF deputy president and party parliamentary chief whip Floyd Shivambu's younger brother Brian has been slapped with two lawsuits by VBS curator Anoosh Rooplal over his R5.5m debt allegedly owed to the collapsed bank. Rooplal filed the two applications at the Joburg High Court on Thursday and in them he sought an order to liquidate Brian's company Sgameka Projects and sequestrate him. TO READ MORE ON THIS STORY GET A COPY OF TODAY'S SUNDAY WORLD